WEBVTT

00:00:01.070 --> 00:00:02.747
Nekada davno,

00:00:02.771 --> 00:00:04.519
bio sam profesionalni animator.

00:00:06.573 --> 00:00:07.723
(Muzika)

00:00:07.747 --> 00:00:09.653
[Erik Dajer]

00:00:09.677 --> 00:00:10.687
[Animator]

00:00:10.711 --> 00:00:11.861
[Kompozitor]

00:00:16.425 --> 00:00:20.132
A noću bih pravio
svoje eksperimentalne filmove.

00:00:20.132 --> 00:00:21.349
(Muzika)

00:00:21.349 --> 00:00:25.914
Provodio sam mnogo vremena,
isuviše vremena, ispred ekrana

00:00:25.914 --> 00:00:28.909
radi dela koje će biti
prikazano na ekranu,

00:00:28.933 --> 00:00:32.656
i imao sam tu veliku potrebu
da ponovo uposlim ruke radom.